Frank R. CREEDON, Housing Expediter (Tighe E. Wood, Acting Housing Expediter, Substituted as Party Appellant), Appellant, v. Clifton L. FENNER, Appellee. No. 12047. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. Nov. 18, 1947. Nathan Siegal, Atty., Office of Rent Control, of Washington, D. C., for appellant. H. S. Beard, of Waco, Tex., for appellee.

Before SIBLEY, HOLMES, and McCORD, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment appealed from is affirmed.
